\c 3
\s Ubizo lukaSamuweli
\p
\v 1 Umfana uSamuweli wayesebenzela iN\nd kosi\nd* phambi kukaEli\x + 2.11,18.\x*. Lelizwi leN\nd kosi\nd* laliligugu ngalezonsuku; kwakungekho lombono osabaleleyo\x + 3.21. Hlab. 74.9. Amos 8.11.\x*.
\p
\v 2 Kwasekusithi ngalolosuku uEli elele endaweni yakhe, lamehlo akhe eseqala ukufiphala engelakubona\x + 4.15. Gen. 27.1. Dute. 34.7. Gen. 48.10.\x*,
\v 3 lesibane sikaNkulunkulu sasingakacitshwa\x + Eks. 27.20,21. Levi 24.2,3. 2 Lan. 13.11.\x*, njalo uSamuweli wayelele ethempelini leN\nd kosi\nd*, lapho okwakukhona umtshokotsho kaNkulunkulu\x + 1.9.\x*,
\v 4 iN\nd kosi\nd* yambiza uSamuweli, owathi: Khangela ngi\add lapha\add*.
\v 5 Wasegijimela kuEli, wathi: Khangela ngi\add lapha\add*, ngoba ungibizile. Wasesithi: Kangibizanga, buyela ulale. Wasesiyalala.
\v 6 IN\nd kosi\nd* yasibuya imbiza uSamuweli futhi. USamuweli wasevuka waya kuEli, wathi: Khangela ngi\add lapha\add*, ngoba ungibizile. Kodwa wathi: Kangibizanga, ndodana yami; buyela ulale.
\v 7 Kodwa uSamuweli wayengakayazi iN\nd kosi\nd*, lelizwi leN\nd kosi\nd* lalingakembulwa kuye.
\v 8 IN\nd kosi\nd* yasimbiza futhi uSamuweli ngokwesithathu. Wasevuka waya kuEli wathi: Khangela ngi\add lapha\add*, ngoba ungibizile. UEli waseqedisisa ukuthi iN\nd kosi\nd* imbizile umfana.
\v 9 Ngakho uEli wathi kuSamuweli: Hamba uyelala; kuzakuthi-ke nxa ikubiza uzakuthi: Khuluma N\nd kosi\nd*, ngoba inceku yakho iyezwa. Wasehamba uSamuweli, walala endaweni yakhe.
\v 10 IN\nd kosi\nd* yasisiza, yema, yabiza njengakwezinye izikhathi: Samuweli, Samuweli! Wasesithi uSamuweli: Khuluma, ngoba inceku yakho iyezwa.
\p
\v 11 IN\nd kosi\nd* yasisithi kuSamuweli: Khangela, ngizakwenza into koIsrayeli ezakhenceza indlebe zombili zalowo wonke oyizwayo\x + 2 Kho. 21.12. Jer. 19.3.\x*.
\v 12 Ngalolosuku ngizakwenza ngimelene loEli konke engakukhuluma ngendlu yakhe; ngiqalise ngiqede\x + 2.27-36.\x*.
\v 13 Ngoba ngimtshelile\x + 2.27-36.\x* ukuthi ngizagweba indlu yakhe kuze kube nininini ngesiphambeko asaziyo\x + Hez. 7.3,8. 18.30. 33.20.\x*, ngoba amadodana akhe azenza aqalekiswa\x + 2.12,17,22.\x*, kodwa kawakhuzanga\x + 2.23-25.\x*.
\v 14 Ngakho-ke ngifungile kuyo indlu kaEli ukuthi ububi bendlu kaEli kabuyikuhlangulwa ngomhlatshelo langomnikelo kuze kube phakade\x + Isa. 22.14.\x*.
\p
\v 15 USamuweli waselala kwaze kwasa; wavula iminyango yendlu yeN\nd kosi\nd*, kodwa uSamuweli wesaba ukumtshela uEli umbono.
\v 16 UEli wasembiza uSamuweli, wathi: Samuweli, ndodana yami. Wasesithi: Khangela ngi\add lapha\add*.
\v 17 Wasesithi: Yinto bani eyikhulume kuwe? Ake ungangifihleli; kenze njalo uNkulunkulu kuwe, ngokunjalo engezelele, uba ungifihlela ulutho lwazo zonke izinto akutshele zona.
\v 18 Ngakho uSamuweli wasemtshela zonke izinto, kamfihlelanga \add lutho\add*. Wasesithi: YiN\nd kosi\nd*, kayenze lokho okulungileyo emehlweni ayo\x + Jobe 1.21. 2.10. Hlab. 39.9. Isa. 39.8.\x*.
\p
\v 19 Wakhula-ke uSamuweli\x + Hlu. 13.24.\x*, leN\nd kosi\nd* yayilaye\x + Gen. 39.2. Josh. 6.27.\x*, kayiyekelanga lelilodwa lamazwi ayo liwele emhlabathini\x + 9.6. Esta 6.10.\x*.
\v 20 UIsrayeli wonke-ke kusukela koDani kuze kube seBherishebha wazi ukuthi uSamuweli uqinisiwe ukuthi abe ngumprofethi weN\nd kosi\x + 2 Sam. 3.10.\x*\nd*.
\v 21 IN\nd kosi\nd* yaphinda yabonakala eShilo, ngoba iN\nd kosi\nd* yazibonakalisa kuSamuweli eShilo\x + Josh. 18.1.\x* ngelizwi leN\nd kosi\x + 3.1,4.\x*\nd*.
